reviews.text:
It's funny. I've never really liked butter pecan ice cream, yet I like everything that goes into it. This, however, is a absolutely sinfully decadent vape. Rich, buttery, pecans that straddle the line between nutty goodness and candy-like praline...and then, there's the cream. A luscious extra creamy vanilla that in no circumstance could be called plain. This is top to bottom an absolute banger of a flavor. If the ice cream actually tasted like this, my beloved Chubby Hubby would be in danger of being replaced.&#xD;
&#xD;
This bad boy is for dessert fans, ice cream idolaters, nut lovers, people who like it buttered, and anyone looking to vape their calories. Seriously, just hit it!&#xD;
&#xD;
Cracking job, JJ.
